    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Offering a driver-spec 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six. This naturally aspirated powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system to produce a linear power band peaking at an 8,000 RPM redline. The visceral mechanical feel is channeled through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis dynamics are sharp, featuring a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension setup. This example is in solid mechanical health; the subframe has been inspected for stress fractures and the VANOS system operates without rattle. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina consistent with its age, the structural integrity and drivetrain performance remain uncompromised. Recent service includes a valve adjustment and fresh fluids throughout.",
